        title "Hardware Security for Symmetric Key-Based Authentication"
        description "This requirement specifies that for devices utilizing symmetric key-based
            +b authentication, hardware mechanisms must be employed to protect these keys from
            +b unauthorized access and use. The aim is to ensure that the symmetric keys
            +b remain confidential and are only accessible to authorized processes and
            +b entities, thereby enhancing the security of authentication mechanisms."
