                reference "Security Requirements for Cryptographic Modules. Provides guidelines for the
                    +b design and implementation of hardware security modules (HSMs) that protect
                    +b cryptographic keys and operations."
            {
                standard "ISO/IEC 19790:2012"
                reference "Security requirements for cryptographic modules. Similar to FIPS 140-3, it
                    +b provides international standards for securing cryptographic modules."
            {
